snippet.title: Monster Mop Up - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now- https://cutt.ly/PwehPqka

The Ministry of Monster Concealment needs you! Grab your mop, gadgets and rescue the Ragamuffins!  

In Monster Mop Up you must locate and save the Ragamuffins, and wipe the evidence of their existence in the human world. Build your home and keep the little Ragamuffins happy!

Follow us for updates:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/terahardstudios
Newsletter: https://cutt.ly/Bwq1ABR8
